         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">1/6/85 ¶  ¶ This time, dear Mr Stephani, only the information that the last mail brought me a very friendly letter from Professor Luerssen, whose longer letter explains the removal and so on by his ta...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">85.06.01a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Franz Stephani</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Conservatoire et Jardin botanique, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">1/6/85</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Diesmal, lieber Herr Stephani, nur die Mittheilung, dass mir die letzte Post einen sehr freundlichen Brief von Hr. Professor Lüerssen</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Luerssen.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> brachte, dessen längeres Schreiben sich durch seine Übernahme der Professur, den Umzug usw. erklärt. Die Neu Guinea Farne kamen richtig bei ihm an. Hoffentlich kann ich auch Ihnen bald wieder neue Materialien für Ihre besonderen Lieblingsstudien senden.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Freundschaftlich Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1/6/85</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This time, dear Mr Stephani, only the information that the last mail brought me a very friendly letter from Professor Luerssen, whose longer letter explains the removal and so on by his taking over the professorship.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found. See M to F. Stephani, 5 April 1885 (in this edition as 85-04-05b), and Stephani's and Luerssen's annotations on it.</p>
               </note> The New Guinea ferns arrived safely at his place. It is to be hoped I can again also send you soon new material for your favourite study.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">In friendship your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
